					<span class="input-group-addon"><i></i></span>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-8 col-md-9">
			<div class="alert alert-danger">
				<a class="close">×</a> <strong>Error</strong> Change a few things up and try submitting again.
